             ADVANCED FRUIT MACHINE SIMULATOR - CODEMASTERS

Typed in by PARASITE of LSD. NOTE: Codemasters, in my opinion are the
best value games producers on the AMIGA and ATARI ST. I hope the game
buyers will carry on supporting this company. If you play pirated
versions of their games, why not buy it, they're only five to seven
quid, damn good value!!!


PLAYING THE GAME

IMPORTANT:
Read the scrolling message during the game, it will lead you through,
and explain what's happening.

Press '1' to start, or '2' - '4' if you want more players.

You can use the mouse or joystick to move the arrow around to control
the game, or use the keys shown below.

MOUSE OR JOYSTICK CONTROL:
Move the arrow around the screen and press a mouse button, or fore on
the joystick when the arrow is pointing where you want.

INSERTING COINS:
Click on the coin pictures at the top of the display. When you've
finished, click on the end icon, to the right of the coins, or on
START, or on TAKE. Also, you can click on the REJECT or GIVE-UP icons
if you want.

DURING THE GAME:
When one of the fruit machine's buttons is flashing, you can press it
by clicking on it.

KEYBOARD CONTROL

INSERTING COINS:

KEY            COIN
1               10p
2               20p
5               50p
0               £1.
T               Token.
R               Reject coins already inserted.
G               Give up.
RETURN/ENTER    When finished.

DURING THE GAME:

KEY          FRUIT MACHINE BUTTON (WHEN FLASHING)
SPACE           Start/Gamble
ENTER/RETURN    Take/Stop
1 2 3           Hold Reel 1 2 3
C               Cancel
SPACE           Shuffle
S               Stake Coin

When one of the Fruit Machines buttons is flashing. You can press the
corresponding key.

FRUIT WINS:

